README.md
     7‚Üí# Soluna
     9‚Üí[‰∏≠Êñá](./README.zh-CN.md)
    10‚Üí
    11‚Üí[Live Examples](https://cloudwu.github.io/soluna/)
    12‚Üí
    13‚ÜíA framework you can use to make 2D games in Lua with multithreading, living on Windows, Linux, macOS and modern Browsers (via WebAssembly).
    14‚Üí
    15‚ÜíIt is built on top of [sokol](https://github.com/floooh/sokol) and leverages the power of ltask for multithreading.
    16‚Üí
    17‚Üí[![Nightly](/../../actions/workflows/nightly.yml/badge.svg)](/../../actions/workflows/nightyly.yml)
